name: GoToZoomOptions
shortdesc: Zoom options for the goto destination page.

property.name: INHERIT_ZOOM
property.shortdesc: Inherits the zoom setting from the previously displayed page.

property.name: FIT_WINDOW
property.shortdesc: Fits the page in the display window.

property.name: FIT_WIDTH
property.shortdesc: Fits the page to the width of the window; may obscure the lower portion of the page.

property.name: FIT_VISIBLE
property.shortdesc: Fits the text area of the page to the window width; obscures page margins and may obscure the lower portion of the page.
